Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:26.86,default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:28.56,default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I can't do it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:29.61,default,,0,0,0,,It's been a year, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:30.96,default,,0,0,0,,For the past year...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:32.85,default,,0,0,0,,I released 3 singles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.15,0:09:35.15,default,,0,0,0,,I was able to go on tours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:37.47,default,,0,0,0,,And now, please stand for the Tokyo Dome performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:39.53,default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:40.56,default,,0,0,0,,I was able to spend a year in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:42.83,default,,0,0,0,,After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:47.21,default,,0,0,0,,I'm very happy to be able to stand on this stage and share the same time with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:50.97,default,,0,0,0,,I'm really looking forward to the live performance after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:56.29,default,,0,0,0,,Today, I'm going to show you the live performance that will be the culmination of this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:59.09,default,,0,0,0,,Are you all ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:07.44,default,,0,0,0,,KURASUKU HOUSE!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.81,0:27:32.81,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming to this venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.79,0:27:35.79,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.10,0:27:37.10,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.78,0:27:44.78,default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.28,0:27:47.28,default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's overseas...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.49,0:28:00.49,default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.52,0:28:01.52,default,,0,0,0,,Since it's a competition...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.15,0:28:04.15,default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you to do the Maton dance in English?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.01,0:28:08.01,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.11,0:28:12.11,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming to our live today.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.31,0:28:15.31,default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to have fun with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.21,0:28:20.21,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.85,0:28:24.85,default,,0,0,0,,It's a pera-pera.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.25,0:28:26.25,default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.95,0:28:27.95,default,,0,0,0,,Last time in Korea too
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.77,0:28:30.77,default,,0,0,0,,Since you said it, Airi-chan, can you say it in Korean?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.77,0:28:32.77,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I want to say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.83,0:28:34.83,default,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.83,0:28:36.07,default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.07,0:28:37.15,default,,0,0,0,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.15,0:28:38.27,default,,0,0,0,,Have you eaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.27,0:28:39.27,default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.26,0:28:41.66,default,,0,0,0,,We, Kokkiriman Kocha, love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.66,0:28:43.66,default,,0,0,0,,Kawaii!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.66,0:28:46.66,default,,0,0,0,,Right now, we're saying hello to BUDDIES.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.66,0:28:48.66,default,,0,0,0,,How are you? Did you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.66,0:28:50.66,default,,0,0,0,,Kawaii!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.66,0:28:54.66,default,,0,0,0,,Let's go down the path of happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.87,0:28:56.87,default,,0,0,0,,Ari-chan, did you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.87,0:28:57.87,default,,0,0,0,,I ate!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.87,0:28:58.87,default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.87,0:28:59.87,default,,0,0,0,,Ari-chan ate!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.87,0:29:00.87,default,,0,0,0,,Everyone ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.87,0:29:01.87,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.87,0:29:06.87,default,,0,0,0,,And at the end of this month, we will be participating in an event in Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.87,0:29:12.87,default,,0,0,0,,The reason we are able to perform overseas is because of BUDDIES' support.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.87,0:29:16.87,default,,0,0,0,,We want to give it our all in Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.87,0:29:18.87,default,,0,0,0,,Since we're here, let's do it in Cantonese.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.87,0:29:22.87,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.87,0:29:24.87,default,,0,0,0,,We love you all! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.36,0:29:28.86,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.86,0:29:32.86,default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd like to ask you again about your enthusiasm for this concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.86,0:29:34.86,default,,0,0,0,,Zono-chan! Ozone!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.86,0:29:36.86,default,,0,0,0,,Zono!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.86,0:29:38.86,default,,0,0,0,,We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.23,0:29:41.23,default,,0,0,0,,I'm 4 years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.97,0:29:45.97,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.79,0:29:46.79,default,,0,0,0,,Ehhhh
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.88,0:29:48.88,default,,0,0,0,,4 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.38,0:29:53.38,default,,0,0,0,,In the first single, there's a song called BUDDIES by TENCHAN CENTER.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.57,0:30:02.17,default,,0,0,0,,We'll sing the song, Nakama Da, and call out to everyone who supports us as BUDDIES.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.17,0:30:04.17,default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.42,0:30:06.92,default,,0,0,0,,We've spent a lot of time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.45,0:30:09.45,default,,0,0,0,,Since the birth of BUDDIES.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.89,0:30:11.89,default,,0,0,0,,I'll be 4 years old, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.00,0:30:14.00,default,,0,0,0,,Should we sing Happy Birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.38,0:30:18.38,default,,0,0,0,,Should we sing Happy Birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.38,0:30:20.38,default,,0,0,0,,Let's do both!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.38,0:30:22.38,default,,0,0,0,,Let's start with Happy Birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.38,0:30:24.38,default,,0,0,0,,Let's sing Happy Birthday and end with Happy Birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.17,0:30:29.17,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.04,0:30:33.04,default,,0,0,0,,Let's sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.25,0:30:39.25,default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.58,0:30:41.58,default,,0,0,0,,Happy Birthday, Dear Buzz!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.48,0:30:58.48,default,,0,0,0,,Let's grow old together!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.48,0:31:00.48,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.57,0:31:03.57,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.53,0:31:05.53,default,,0,0,0,,Everyone here today is 4 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.53,0:31:06.53,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.53,0:31:11.53,default,,0,0,0,,It's a group, so I'd like to celebrate and have fun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.53,0:31:12.53,default,,0,0,0,,One more person, Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.53,0:31:13.53,default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.89,0:31:15.89,default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Mino!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.39,0:31:20.89,default,,0,0,0,,I was really into it from the start
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.89,0:31:22.89,default,,0,0,0,,I said thank you earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.89,0:31:24.89,default,,0,0,0,,But I was more like
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.89,0:31:26.89,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.89,0:31:33.89,default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a voice that's as loud as me?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.89,0:31:34.89,default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.97,0:31:43.97,default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.29,0:31:46.29,default,,0,0,0,,I felt it in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.29,0:31:54.29,default,,0,0,0,,At the beginning, I was at the end of my left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.29,0:32:00.29,default,,0,0,0,,I was there, but I should have been a little closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.29,0:32:07.29,default,,0,0,0,,But when I saw the BUDDIES,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.13,0:32:10.13,default,,0,0,0,,I have to get closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.44,0:32:15.44,default,,0,0,0,,That's how much I'm into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.44,0:32:17.44,default,,0,0,0,,Let's all have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.44,0:32:18.44,default,,0,0,0,,Let's have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.51,0:32:23.51,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right. All the members are full of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.51,0:32:27.51,default,,0,0,0,,I want to have a fun time with everyone here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.51,0:32:31.51,default,,0,0,0,,And we will deliver the best live performance of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.51,0:32:33.51,default,,0,0,0,,Are you all ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.56,0:32:36.56,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.00,0:32:39.36,default,,0,0,0,,After this, let's all have fun together!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.23,0:42:05.23,default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.15,0:46:55.15,default,,0,0,0,,In the scenery
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.86,0:47:00.86,default,,0,0,0,,We also receive a lot of power. Thank you very much as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.76,0:47:08.76,default,,0,0,0,,We were able to perform a few of those songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.09,0:47:11.09,default,,0,0,0,,How was it so far, Mi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.90,0:47:13.90,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.15,0:47:15.15,default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.52,0:47:17.52,default,,0,0,0,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.22,0:47:18.22,default,,0,0,0,,Can I talk about what I'm thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.22,0:47:19.22,default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.22,0:47:23.22,default,,0,0,0,,Last year, I was in this ZOZO MARIE STUDIO...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.74,0:47:28.74,default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to stand up and I was looking at everyone from the audience seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.02,0:47:37.66,default,,0,0,0,,At that time, to be honest, I thought that I might not be able to go back to Sakurazaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.40,0:47:39.40,default,,0,0,0,,The end.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.61,0:47:40.11,default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.89,0:47:43.89,default,,0,0,0,,Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.43,0:47:48.43,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.37,0:47:51.37,default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.04,0:47:54.54,default,,0,0,0,,All the members were so warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.45,0:47:59.45,default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was so warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.73,0:48:02.73,default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.01,0:48:04.01,default,,0,0,0,,I thought about a lot of things, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.73,0:48:06.73,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.88,0:48:10.64,default,,0,0,0,,I want to do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.78,0:48:15.94,default,,0,0,0,,I'm very happy to be able to celebrate my 4th anniversary here,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.94,0:48:21.54,default,,0,0,0,,and I'm very happy to be able to meet everyone and be on stage with all the members.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.92,0:48:23.92,default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.16,0:48:26.16,default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.73,0:48:26.23,default,,0,0,0,,Teh!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.48,0:48:30.48,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, everyone, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.46,0:48:32.46,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.25,0:48:34.25,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.02,0:48:39.02,default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for this for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.02,0:48:41.52,default,,0,0,0,,This year, being able to stand with Min-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.52,0:48:43.52,default,,0,0,0,,the members, and BUDDIES,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.52,0:48:45.52,default,,0,0,0,,we're happy happy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.25,0:48:50.65,default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy! Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.65,0:48:51.85,default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best together!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.85,0:48:52.65,default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.65,0:48:54.85,default,,0,0,0,,Next is...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.85,0:48:55.65,default,,0,0,0,,Yutan!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.90,0:48:57.90,default,,0,0,0,,You should have said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.90,0:48:59.90,default,,0,0,0,,I said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.70,0:49:01.70,default,,0,0,0,,Yuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.79,0:49:03.79,default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.94,0:49:04.94,default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.53,0:49:07.53,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.49,0:49:09.49,default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine too!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.04,0:49:13.04,default,,0,0,0,,I love it when Kyo comes
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.16,0:49:14.16,default,,0,0,0,,I was really looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.16,0:49:21.16,default,,0,0,0,,I remember last year's 3rd anniversary live very vividly,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.16,0:49:27.16,default,,0,0,0,,and I've been working hard on it for the past year.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.16,0:49:30.16,default,,0,0,0,,At the last year's anniversary live,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.16,0:49:33.16,default,,0,0,0,,I was able to see the color of the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.31,0:49:36.71,default,,0,0,0,,I could really feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.34,0:49:39.34,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.91,0:49:44.65,default,,0,0,0,,The choreography, the production, and the live performances we've done with Team Sakurazaka 46.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.65,0:49:47.35,default,,0,0,0,,When we did it on stage, the BUDDIES were like,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.35,0:49:49.43,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is how it's going to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.43,0:49:52.31,default,,0,0,0,,I felt like, Oh, this is how it's going to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.31,0:49:57.11,default,,0,0,0,,I felt like, Oh, this is how BUDDIES and I are going to make a live performance together.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.11,0:49:58.87,default,,0,0,0,,I felt that a lot last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.87,0:50:02.31,default,,0,0,0,,I was really looking forward to Kyoga-kun this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.31,0:50:04.31,default,,0,0,0,,Did you all look forward to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.86,0:50:06.86,default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.14,0:50:20.94,default,,0,0,0,,I'm very grateful and happy that there are songs that can be delivered in a new way this time as well as songs that can be performed for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.28,0:50:23.28,default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of Hatsuhiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.88,0:50:28.88,default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of the 3rd generation song, Honitsu-Teki na Koto, performed by Riko-chan of CENTER?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.88,0:50:30.88,default,,0,0,0,,Riko-chan of CENTER!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.88,0:50:32.88,default,,0,0,0,,I got goose bumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.88,0:50:34.88,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.88,0:50:42.88,default,,0,0,0,,At first, there was a scene where I walked from the CENTER stage to the main stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.88,0:50:46.88,default,,0,0,0,,If I were a year ago, I wouldn't have imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.88,0:50:48.88,default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.19,0:50:49.69,default,,0,0,0,,360 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.69,0:50:51.69,default,,0,0,0,,The PUDDYs are...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.68,0:50:55.68,default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined that I would be walking alone in a place where so many people are gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.68,0:50:57.68,default,,0,0,0,,I was very surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.95,0:51:02.55,default,,0,0,0,,I was a bit nervous, but most of all, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.78,0:51:08.78,default,,0,0,0,,I would like to perform my favorite songs in front of my beloved BUDDIES.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.21,0:51:12.21,default,,0,0,0,,I felt very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.21,0:51:15.21,default,,0,0,0,,The members were also very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.61,0:51:17.61,default,,0,0,0,,BUDDIES,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.05,0:51:20.05,default,,0,0,0,,I really like this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.32,0:51:22.32,default,,0,0,0,,She said she likes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.32,0:51:24.32,default,,0,0,0,,She said she likes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.32,0:51:26.32,default,,0,0,0,,Every time I hear that, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.42,0:51:29.42,default,,0,0,0,,I like this song more and more
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.44,0:51:37.04,default,,0,0,0,,I want to do my best to make it a song that will be loved by everyone in the future as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.04,0:51:41.04,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.71,0:51:41.71,default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.69,0:51:43.69,default,,0,0,0,,Riko-chan, you like this song, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.69,0:51:45.69,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.69,0:51:48.69,default,,0,0,0,,Many seniors say they like this song, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.69,0:51:50.69,default,,0,0,0,,I like it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.69,0:51:52.69,default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.69,0:51:54.69,default,,0,0,0,,Rina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.69,0:51:56.69,default,,0,0,0,,Akiho-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.69,0:51:58.69,default,,0,0,0,,Akiho-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.69,0:52:00.69,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.69,0:52:05.69,default,,0,0,0,,I was looking forward to seeing you perform today.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.69,0:52:09.69,default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to perform here for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.47,0:52:11.87,default,,0,0,0,,There's one more member I'd like to ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.87,0:52:13.87,default,,0,0,0,,Rina-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.30,0:52:16.30,default,,0,0,0,,It's our 40th anniversary, how do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.30,0:52:18.30,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.08,0:52:21.60,default,,0,0,0,,Until last year's 3rd anniversary...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.89,0:52:35.74,default,,0,0,0,,I think there were a lot of times when we were divided into 1st and 2nd generation songs and 3rd generation songs, but in the 4th year this year, there were a lot of live performances from January, and the live rehearsal
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.84,0:52:40.84,default,,0,0,0,,I spend most of my time with the members, from morning to night.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.84,0:52:42.84,default,,0,0,0,,All three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.69,0:52:50.41,default,,0,0,0,,We've spent a lot of time together, and I think we've gotten really close.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.28,0:52:51.28,default,,0,0,0,,So today...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.49,0:52:51.69,default,,0,0,0,,From the first song.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.97,0:52:55.97,default,,0,0,0,,In the second song, there was a song with all of us, and it was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.61,0:53:02.25,default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy that we were able to make a song together for the 4th anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.49,0:53:04.49,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.49,0:53:08.49,default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was really involved in the fan meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.54,0:53:09.98,default,,0,0,0,,We're very happy about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.98,0:53:11.98,default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the other Senpais too, how should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.98,0:53:13.98,default,,0,0,0,,This year, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.49,0:53:18.27,default,,0,0,0,,I think I was able to deepen the bond between the seniors and juniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.27,0:53:26.11,default,,0,0,0,,I think this year was a year when I was able to deepen the bond and trust between the members.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.30,0:53:34.80,default,,0,0,0,,Today is the last day of the year, so I'd like to have a great time with all the members and BUDDIES.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.80,0:53:35.80,default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.48,0:53:38.48,default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.18,0:53:45.18,default,,0,0,0,,Let's celebrate Terazaka46's anniversary together!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.85,0:53:47.85,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.55,0:53:50.05,default,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy the rest of the show!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.20,1:28:19.00,default,,0,0,0,,During the MC, we were able to remember the things we love and the memories of this year.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.61,1:28:22.61,default,,0,0,0,,While feeling fun and happiness
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.62,1:28:25.82,default,,0,0,0,,I hope you enjoy the live performance.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.11,1:28:28.11,default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.68,1:28:29.68,default,,0,0,0,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.68,1:28:31.68,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.68,1:28:38.68,default,,0,0,0,,In this MC, I would like to ask the members about their memories of this year.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.68,1:28:40.68,default,,0,0,0,,First of all,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.07,1:28:43.77,default,,0,0,0,,Miu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.77,1:28:45.77,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm Miu Murayama.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.77,1:28:47.77,default,,0,0,0,,Miu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.77,1:28:51.77,default,,0,0,0,,This year, SAKURAZAKA...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.32,1:28:55.32,default,,0,0,0,,This year, I was able to experience the kindness of people.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.55,1:28:59.55,default,,0,0,0,,I think it was a year when I felt that way and was saved.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.41,1:29:04.31,default,,0,0,0,,I tend to get really nervous.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.31,1:29:04.81,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.81,1:29:06.81,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I tend to get nervous.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.81,1:29:08.51,default,,0,0,0,,I tend to get nervous, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.51,1:29:13.11,default,,0,0,0,,At that time, there was someone who told me to enjoy being nervous.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.44,1:29:15.44,default,,0,0,0,,That's all I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.74,1:29:17.74,default,,0,0,0,,I was saved.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.05,1:29:20.05,default,,0,0,0,,so that you can enjoy the tension little by little.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.54,1:29:22.54,default,,0,0,0,,That's how it has become.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.98,1:29:27.98,default,,0,0,0,,Ruto...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.94,1:29:28.94,default,,0,0,0,,The moment I dropped it, it was like...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.18,1:29:31.18,default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm going to cry.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.10,1:29:33.70,default,,0,0,0,,There are times when it gets hard, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.05,1:29:36.05,default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.68,1:29:39.28,default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's just for a moment, I will never leave Sakurazaka alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.45,1:29:40.95,default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.53,1:29:43.53,default,,0,0,0,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.65,1:29:45.65,default,,0,0,0,,How do I say this?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.09,1:29:47.09,default,,0,0,0,,Where will you be by my side?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.55,1:29:50.91,default,,0,0,0,,I really love that side of Sakurazaka.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.42,1:29:53.42,default,,0,0,0,,The kindness I received...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.95,1:29:56.95,default,,0,0,0,,I want to be a person who can connect with others.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.21,1:29:59.21,default,,0,0,0,,I think it's very strong, recently.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.00,1:30:02.00,default,,0,0,0,,See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.08,1:30:03.08,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.45,1:30:12.09,default,,0,0,0,,Miyu said it too, but in Sakurazaka, everyone is so considerate and kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.09,1:30:20.09,default,,0,0,0,,Miyu said she was kind, but we get a lot of kindness from Miyu, so thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.09,1:30:23.09,default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.09,1:30:23.93,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.93,1:30:32.81,default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure everyone knows Miyu's kindness, but we love Miyu too.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.81,1:30:34.81,default,,0,0,0,,Let's continue to walk together.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.81,1:30:36.81,default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.81,1:30:38.81,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.37,1:30:42.37,default,,0,0,0,,I'll listen to the other person's song.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.29,1:30:45.29,default,,0,0,0,,Yu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.54,1:30:46.54,default,,0,0,0,,I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.33,1:30:46.83,default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.74,1:30:49.74,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.29,1:30:58.29,default,,0,0,0,,Looking back on this year, I think I've grown a lot this year.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.53,1:31:00.53,default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that is.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.47,1:31:05.87,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how I can contribute more to SAKURAZAKA
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.92,1:31:07.92,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.90,1:31:09.90,default,,0,0,0,,I'll do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.92,1:31:16.92,default,,0,0,0,,It was a year when I thought about what I could do for the group.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.95,1:31:19.95,default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.01,1:31:22.61,default,,0,0,0,,Last year's anniversary live was probably...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.10,1:31:25.10,default,,0,0,0,,Rather than that, I'd like to participate now.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.77,1:31:28.77,default,,0,0,0,,Thankfully, the number of songs has increased.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.96,1:31:30.96,default,,0,0,0,,It's not just that, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.81,1:31:33.81,default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.12,1:31:36.12,default,,0,0,0,,But the most important thing for me is...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.67,1:31:38.67,default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.34,1:31:39.34,default,,0,0,0,,Not last year, but at the beginning of this year.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.65,1:31:45.65,default,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi-san's graduation concert was a big deal for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.55,1:31:49.55,default,,0,0,0,,What was it? The group...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.14,1:31:52.54,default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm being supported.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.96,1:31:54.96,default,,0,0,0,,For that reason, or...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.72,1:31:58.72,default,,0,0,0,,It's for my own sake, but it's also for the sake of the group.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.59,1:32:00.59,default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.38,1:32:07.38,default,,0,0,0,,He was a person who thought a lot about what I could do and supported me, and when I saw his big back, I thought that I could do it too.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.33,1:32:10.67,default,,0,0,0,,That's what I really wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.09,1:32:14.09,default,,0,0,0,,What is it? I also...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.79,1:32:18.11,default,,0,0,0,,It's difficult, but I get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.58,1:32:24.78,default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there will be new members next year,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.78,1:32:30.78,default,,0,0,0,,but I want them to be able to do something for their big back and the group.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.81,1:32:34.81,default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to keep that feeling in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.49,1:32:37.49,default,,0,0,0,,I want to keep that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.89,1:32:44.39,default,,0,0,0,,I think it was a very big thing in this year that I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.39,1:32:46.39,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.39,1:32:48.39,default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I couldn't put it together.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.39,1:32:58.89,default,,0,0,0,,Certainly, Yui's graduation concert, Kobayashi's graduation concert, and Uemura and Fuuka's graduation.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.89,1:33:08.89,default,,0,0,0,,This time, we're in a position to be seniors, so I hope we can show our big backs like Yui said.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.17,1:33:16.17,default,,0,0,0,,This year was a year where I felt that there were a lot of big evolutions and changes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.99,1:33:24.35,default,,0,0,0,,Up until a year ago, the three of us would talk a lot and share a lot of emotions.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.67,1:33:31.11,default,,0,0,0,,Recently, I've been able to share a lot of fun and sad things with my seniors.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.11,1:33:41.99,default,,0,0,0,,I often have the opportunity to say to the BUDDIES that Sakurazaka46 is very close to their seniors and juniors.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.99,1:33:51.43,default,,0,0,0,,The seniors are really kind, and we've grown up watching them.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.43,1:34:05.43,default,,0,0,0,,I hope that the charm of Sakurazaka46 will continue to be transmitted to the new 4th generation and the BUDDIES, along with the good changes and evolutions.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.43,1:34:11.03,default,,0,0,0,,And Sakurazaka46 in 2024 is not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.03,1:34:13.03,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.90,1:34:15.30,default,,0,0,0,,The 4th year anniversary tour is still going on!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.30,1:34:17.30,default,,0,0,0,,Buddies!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.83,1:34:18.83,default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to get fired up!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:32.38,2:23:34.38,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:33.02,2:23:35.62,default,,0,0,0,,To everyone in the back seats, stand-by, and in the front seats...
Dialogue: 0,2:23:44.61,2:23:46.61,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:46.62,2:23:48.62,default,,0,0,0,,I was really happy
Dialogue: 0,2:23:48.16,2:23:52.76,default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask the members their thoughts on today's performance.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:53.09,2:23:55.09,default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:53.79,2:23:54.59,default,,0,0,0,,Shizuki!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:54.59,2:23:56.59,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm Yamashita Shizuki.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:57.15,2:24:06.75,default,,0,0,0,,Well, since I woke up this morning, I thought that the 4th anniversary live would be over in these two days.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:06.75,2:24:13.87,default,,0,0,0,,I was very lonely, so I thought that I would like to take advantage of it while riding the float, but
Dialogue: 0,2:24:13.87,2:24:19.15,default,,0,0,0,,there were a lot of songs that I performed for the first time in this live, but
Dialogue: 0,2:24:19.15,2:24:25.99,default,,0,0,0,,the 10th single that I performed at the end earlier, I want tomorrow to come, but
Dialogue: 0,2:24:25.99,2:24:33.59,default,,0,0,0,,Sakurazaka's big venue, Sakurazaka's overall live, for the first time
Dialogue: 0,2:24:32.13,2:24:36.33,default,,0,0,0,,It was a great opportunity for me to show my talent to the world.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:37.18,2:24:46.78,default,,0,0,0,,I love this song very much, and there are a lot of days when I don't want tomorrow to come,
Dialogue: 0,2:24:46.78,2:24:53.46,default,,0,0,0,,but I'm sure everyone who came here had such a day at least once.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:53.46,2:24:55.46,default,,0,0,0,,On such a day...
Dialogue: 0,2:24:55.74,2:24:57.74,default,,0,0,0,,This song...
Dialogue: 0,2:24:58.30,2:25:00.30,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:00.99,2:25:01.99,default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:01.99,2:25:02.99,default,,0,0,0,,We met, right?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:02.99,2:25:03.99,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we met.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:03.99,2:25:05.99,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we met.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:16.41,2:25:17.41,default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:21.95,2:25:23.95,default,,0,0,0,,I'm really...
Dialogue: 0,2:25:23.84,2:25:25.84,default,,0,0,0,,Listen to this song.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:25.76,2:25:27.76,default,,0,0,0,,I feel like my heart has been saved.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:27.68,2:25:29.68,default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,2:25:28.64,2:25:30.64,default,,0,0,0,,I hope you feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:31.01,2:25:33.01,default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,2:25:32.32,2:25:34.32,default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:33.85,2:25:35.85,default,,0,0,0,,That's what I wanted to show you today.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:36.67,2:25:37.67,default,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:37.82,2:25:40.62,default,,0,0,0,,I like the band called Sakurazaka.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:40.77,2:25:42.77,default,,0,0,0,,and all of you who have gathered here today.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:42.78,2:25:48.78,default,,0,0,0,,We also love the group, and it's a place where we can share what we like with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:49.28,2:25:52.28,default,,0,0,0,,I think it's wonderful that it happens so many times a year.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:52.67,2:25:54.67,default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:54.24,2:26:03.24,default,,0,0,0,,I've been so happy for the past two days, and 2020 is not over yet, but it's a year that I've come to realize a lot.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:03.74,2:26:05.74,default,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:04.96,2:26:06.96,default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful view.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:06.62,2:26:12.22,default,,0,0,0,,It was really fun. Thank you very much for today.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:16.41,2:26:18.41,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:17.63,2:26:21.43,default,,0,0,0,,There was Shizuki's center, so Aori was really cool, too.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:21.43,2:26:23.43,default,,0,0,0,,It was cool.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:23.43,2:26:25.43,default,,0,0,0,,It was a blast.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:25.43,2:26:27.43,default,,0,0,0,,It was a blast.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:27.43,2:26:29.43,default,,0,0,0,,It was the best. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:29.28,2:26:31.28,default,,0,0,0,,Next, Ten-chan!
Dialogue: 0,2:26:32.38,2:26:34.38,default,,0,0,0,,I'm Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,2:26:35.42,2:26:37.42,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,2:26:36.54,2:26:38.54,default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I've done it, but...
Dialogue: 0,2:26:38.11,2:26:39.41,default,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:39.41,2:26:40.61,default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:42.11,2:26:42.81,default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:42.81,2:26:44.61,default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk seriously, then.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:44.61,2:26:45.41,default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,2:26:45.41,2:26:48.01,default,,0,0,0,,Since it's Sakurazaka's 4th anniversary,
Dialogue: 0,2:26:48.01,2:26:51.81,default,,0,0,0,,I thought back on a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:52.35,2:26:53.35,default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:53.44,2:26:56.44,default,,0,0,0,,When I just made my debut, I was quite...
Dialogue: 0,2:26:56.64,2:27:04.20,default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's going to happen in the future, and I wonder what sakurazakarashisa is, while searching for that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:04.45,2:27:09.77,default,,0,0,0,,There were times when I was anxious, but I wonder why I was able to come this far.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:10.11,2:27:12.11,default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:11.49,2:27:13.49,default,,0,0,0,,BUDDIES!
Dialogue: 0,2:27:13.31,2:27:15.31,default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be better than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:15.97,2:27:17.97,default,,0,0,0,,and cheering me on.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:18.21,2:27:28.21,default,,0,0,0,,I think we were able to come this far because we wanted to meet everyone's expectations.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:28.21,2:27:31.21,default,,0,0,0,,I want to express my gratitude for everyone's daily life.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:31.29,2:27:38.13,default,,0,0,0,,I think it's a wonderful place where you can express your gratitude directly at a live performance.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:38.94,2:27:40.94,default,,0,0,0,,All the BUDDIES out there...
Dialogue: 0,2:27:40.99,2:27:43.99,default,,0,0,0,,They look so happy when they see us,
Dialogue: 0,2:27:43.99,2:27:47.99,default,,0,0,0,,and they look so happy when they call us.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:48.16,2:27:53.86,default,,0,0,0,,It would be nice if I could return the favor a little.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:53.86,2:27:55.86,default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,2:27:55.45,2:27:57.45,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:57.05,2:27:59.05,default,,0,0,0,,BUDDIES, thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,2:27:59.45,2:28:01.45,default,,0,0,0,,I think there are times when it's hard.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:01.92,2:28:07.92,default,,0,0,0,,When Sakurazaka was in a pinch or when we needed help,
Dialogue: 0,2:28:07.92,2:28:11.28,default,,0,0,0,,BUDDIES were there to help us.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:11.71,2:28:15.71,default,,0,0,0,,When we, BUDDIES, are in a pinch, we'll be there for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:14.40,2:28:18.40,default,,0,0,0,,Stay close to your heart, even if it's just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:18.33,2:28:20.33,default,,0,0,0,,It makes me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:20.61,2:28:22.61,default,,0,0,0,,It's like a place in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:22.43,2:28:24.43,default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:23.13,2:28:27.13,default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could be in a group like that.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:27.42,2:28:29.42,default,,0,0,0,,That's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:29.21,2:28:32.73,default,,0,0,0,,I want to do my best in the future as well.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:33.60,2:28:35.60,default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:34.56,2:28:37.56,default,,0,0,0,,It's my 5th year, so from now on, Sakurazaka!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:38.21,2:28:40.21,default,,0,0,0,,It's not what you think it is!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:40.45,2:28:41.15,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:41.15,2:28:42.15,default,,0,0,0,,Your voice echoes.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:42.95,2:28:44.15,default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:45.15,2:28:47.15,default,,0,0,0,,I suddenly get excited.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:48.15,2:28:49.45,default,,0,0,0,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:49.95,2:28:51.95,default,,0,0,0,,By all means!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:50.65,2:28:52.65,default,,0,0,0,,By all means!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:51.45,2:28:53.45,default,,0,0,0,,By all means!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:52.19,2:28:55.59,default,,0,0,0,,I want to deliver as much as I can
Dialogue: 0,2:28:56.00,2:28:58.00,default,,0,0,0,,By all means!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:57.02,2:28:59.02,default,,0,0,0,,By all means, by all means, by all means, by all means,
Dialogue: 0,2:28:59.02,2:29:00.02,default,,0,0,0,,By all means, by all means, by all means,
Dialogue: 0,2:29:00.02,2:29:06.02,default,,0,0,0,,I hope you will continue to watch over us from now on.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:06.02,2:29:08.02,default,,0,0,0,,We won't let you down.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:08.13,2:29:10.13,default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm going to do.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:09.34,2:29:11.34,default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm prepared for.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:12.09,2:29:12.59,default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:12.59,2:29:14.09,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:14.09,2:29:16.09,default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad to hear that, P-chan!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:17.41,2:29:20.41,default,,0,0,0,,That's why I don't want to change my name from Sakurazaka to Oshihen!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:25.73,2:29:26.73,default,,0,0,0,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:26.73,2:29:27.73,default,,0,0,0,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:27.73,2:29:28.73,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:28.73,2:29:31.73,default,,0,0,0,,We received a lot of power today.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:31.73,2:29:34.73,default,,0,0,0,,We'll give you a lot more power.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:34.73,2:29:36.73,default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful on your way home.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:37.73,2:29:38.73,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:38.73,2:29:39.73,default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:39.73,2:29:40.73,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:40.73,2:29:41.73,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:41.73,2:29:43.73,default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of Sen-chan-ness.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:44.73,2:29:45.73,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:45.73,2:29:46.73,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:46.40,2:29:48.40,default,,0,0,0,,Lastly, Hono-chan!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:48.40,2:29:50.40,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm Hono-chan!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:51.26,2:29:53.26,default,,0,0,0,,After Ten-chan, it's tough!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:56.26,2:30:01.26,default,,0,0,0,,I also wanted to say something, but I thought it was similar to Ten-chan.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:01.26,2:30:09.26,default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that I felt the same way in a good way.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:09.26,2:30:11.26,default,,0,0,0,,I've been doing it since the first single.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:12.22,2:30:16.02,default,,0,0,0,,I've been doing it for four years, and I'm about to enter my fifth year.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:16.02,2:30:17.50,default,,0,0,0,,That's the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:17.50,2:30:20.34,default,,0,0,0,,There's something about Sakurazaka and Tsuyomi.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:20.93,2:30:21.93,default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:21.63,2:30:23.63,default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:23.17,2:30:28.01,default,,0,0,0,,We're doing it desperately, but when we're asked that, it's very difficult to answer in words.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:28.01,2:30:31.17,default,,0,0,0,,There was a time when I thought.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:30.05,2:30:32.05,default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,2:30:30.75,2:30:32.75,default,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to the members.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:36.57,2:30:38.57,default,,0,0,0,,It's like...
Dialogue: 0,2:30:37.18,2:30:40.38,default,,0,0,0,,The reason why we are standing here today is because...
Dialogue: 0,2:30:40.96,2:30:44.96,default,,0,0,0,,We are standing here today because we are all standing together,
Dialogue: 0,2:30:44.96,2:30:48.96,default,,0,0,0,,and we are all standing together,
Dialogue: 0,2:30:48.96,2:30:50.96,default,,0,0,0,,and we are all standing together,
Dialogue: 0,2:30:51.04,2:30:56.24,default,,0,0,0,,They've been supporting us as we are, and that's why we're doing what we're doing now.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:56.54,2:30:59.38,default,,0,0,0,,I'm standing on this stage as I am.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:00.29,2:31:02.29,default,,0,0,0,,How do I put this, you guys are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:01.89,2:31:03.89,default,,0,0,0,,There are so many different characters.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:03.36,2:31:14.36,default,,0,0,0,,I'm a member of Sakura-Zaka, but I've recently come to think that it's Sakura-Zaka to be able to stay in this place as it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:14.36,2:31:20.36,default,,0,0,0,,I personally feel that it is thanks to BUDDIES and the members.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:20.41,2:31:22.41,default,,0,0,0,,I'm here for you, BUDDIES.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:23.23,2:31:25.23,default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Life is already...
Dialogue: 0,2:31:24.77,2:31:27.77,default,,0,0,0,,I think there are a lot of things, like work and school.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:28.16,2:31:33.04,default,,0,0,0,,I think it really depends on each person, but in your lives, we, SAKURAZAKA,
Dialogue: 0,2:31:33.04,2:31:38.00,default,,0,0,0,,will support you and support you, so let's support each other like that.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:38.62,2:31:45.62,default,,0,0,0,,I want to be in a group where I can live my life while pushing, pushing, pushing, pushing.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:45.92,2:31:47.92,default,,0,0,0,,At the end of the day, we were all like...
Dialogue: 0,2:31:48.38,2:31:56.98,default,,0,0,0,,I was doing it with my hands tied up in the flow, but I really felt like I was doing it with all the BUDDIES here and all the BUDDIES who are watching the stream.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:57.44,2:31:59.44,default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:58.14,2:32:00.14,default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying, I'm holding your hand
Dialogue: 0,2:32:00.54,2:32:05.18,default,,0,0,0,,I was there. I was actually holding hands with everyone, so that's about it.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:05.47,2:32:08.47,default,,0,0,0,,I love you all and I truly trust you all.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:08.73,2:32:11.93,default,,0,0,0,,I hope you will continue to look forward to us.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:12.57,2:32:15.17,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your continued support of SAKURAZAKA.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:15.17,2:32:17.17,default,,0,0,0,,I love you so much!
Dialogue: 0,2:32:17.31,2:32:19.31,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for today.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:23.65,2:32:25.65,default,,0,0,0,,It's really...
Dialogue: 0,2:32:24.99,2:32:26.99,default,,0,0,0,,The story of the three people I just heard
Dialogue: 0,2:32:27.65,2:32:31.65,default,,0,0,0,,I think it's up to each member to have their own opinion.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:31.93,2:32:33.93,default,,0,0,0,,We're always Buddies.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:33.95,2:32:37.95,default,,0,0,0,,We often talk about how much we love you,
Dialogue: 0,2:32:37.95,2:32:44.95,default,,0,0,0,,and today we were able to celebrate Sakura-zaka and BUDDY's 4th birthday together.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:44.95,2:32:46.95,default,,0,0,0,,It was really fun.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:46.95,2:32:48.95,default,,0,0,0,,A little bug came in though.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:50.95,2:32:51.95,default,,0,0,0,,It's a little...
Dialogue: 0,2:32:52.95,2:32:54.95,default,,0,0,0,,BUDDY's have increased.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:54.95,2:32:56.95,default,,0,0,0,,BUDDY's have increased.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:56.95,2:32:57.95,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:59.95,2:33:01.95,default,,0,0,0,,We talked about it yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,2:33:01.95,2:33:06.95,default,,0,0,0,,but I think that the present is really wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:06.95,2:33:10.95,default,,0,0,0,,The past, the future, and the present.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:10.95,2:33:17.95,default,,0,0,0,,Every moment is a moment when we face each other wholeheartedly and deliver with all our might.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:17.95,2:33:19.95,default,,0,0,0,,I hope that everyone...
Dialogue: 0,2:33:19.52,2:33:26.52,default,,0,0,0,,What you've seen and felt about Sakurazaka is important to you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,2:33:26.85,2:33:28.85,default,,0,0,0,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,2:33:27.58,2:33:33.30,default,,0,0,0,,I think it would be great if it could be a happy memory or a wonderful memory.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:33.30,2:33:39.46,default,,0,0,0,,Recently, I've been getting a lot of expectations from BUDDIES.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:39.71,2:33:51.71,default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want to live up to everyone's expectations, but I also want to live up to everyone's expectations more and more in the future.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:51.71,2:33:59.71,default,,0,0,0,,But for that, I think the growth of the group is necessary, but compared to last year, I think Sakurazaka has grown a little.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:59.90,2:34:02.38,default,,0,0,0,,No, I think we're definitely growing.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:02.38,2:34:06.66,default,,0,0,0,,But that growth is because each member has grown.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:06.66,2:34:09.02,default,,0,0,0,,It's also connected to the growth of the group.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:09.02,2:34:11.02,default,,0,0,0,,But it's not just us.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:11.02,2:34:18.38,default,,0,0,0,,I think BUDDIES have their own lives and their own growth.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:18.59,2:34:20.59,default,,0,0,0,,That's why we are...
Dialogue: 0,2:34:20.93,2:34:22.93,default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,2:34:21.95,2:34:23.95,default,,0,0,0,,SAKURA ZAKATO BUDDIES!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:23.45,2:34:33.45,default,,0,0,0,,For me, it's like walking side by side and walking together.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:35.52,2:34:37.52,default,,0,0,0,,I still have a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:37.50,2:34:40.42,default,,0,0,0,,I think there are still a lot of sceneries that I haven't seen yet.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:40.42,2:34:44.06,default,,0,0,0,,So I want to take a picture with you all.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:44.86,2:34:45.86,default,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,2:34:46.30,2:34:52.86,default,,0,0,0,,As long as there is Sakurazaka, I don't think there is a goal.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:53.25,2:34:54.25,default,,0,0,0,,So that's...
Dialogue: 0,2:34:54.37,2:35:01.37,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I can say it well, but for example, I was very happy to be able to stand on the Tokyo Dome, and it was my goal.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:01.44,2:35:03.44,default,,0,0,0,,But, like...
Dialogue: 0,2:35:03.23,2:35:03.73,default,,0,0,0,,Right there!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:04.00,2:35:08.00,default,,0,0,0,,So I think there is a way up, or a way forward.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:08.38,2:35:11.10,default,,0,0,0,,That's why I have Sakurazaka!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:11.26,2:35:13.26,default,,0,0,0,,Scenery I haven't seen yet?
Dialogue: 0,2:35:13.28,2:35:21.28,default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want to go see it a lot with Men-san.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:21.50,2:35:32.50,default,,0,0,0,,From now on, Sakurazaka46 will continue to deliver exciting things and things that will be of help to everyone, so please look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:32.09,2:35:35.09,default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to walk with me to Sakurazaka?
Dialogue: 0,2:35:35.55,2:35:37.55,default,,0,0,0,,Ayamu!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:36.51,2:35:38.51,default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:38.51,2:35:40.51,default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:40.51,2:35:42.51,default,,0,0,0,,We're buddies!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:42.51,2:35:44.51,default,,0,0,0,,We've been buddies since yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:44.51,2:35:45.51,default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:45.51,2:35:46.51,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:46.51,2:35:47.51,default,,0,0,0,,Forever!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:47.51,2:35:48.51,default,,0,0,0,,Forever!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:48.51,2:35:51.51,default,,0,0,0,,Sakurazaka and Buddies are forever!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:51.51,2:35:52.51,default,,0,0,0,,For the 5th year!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:52.51,2:35:54.51,default,,0,0,0,,For the 5th year, Sakurazaka 46!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:54.51,2:35:56.51,default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of us!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:56.51,2:35:58.51,default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of us!
Dialogue: 0,2:36:03.07,2:36:07.07,default,,0,0,0,,The next song is going to be the last one.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:07.07,2:36:11.07,default,,0,0,0,,Who wants to have fun with me?
Dialogue: 0,2:36:11.36,2:36:13.36,default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,2:36:13.57,2:36:15.57,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,2:36:17.53,2:36:20.33,default,,0,0,0,,Can you make it cherry blossom pink?
Dialogue: 0,2:36:21.79,2:36:23.79,default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot in pink, too.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:27.71,2:36:29.71,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,2:36:29.57,2:36:31.57,default,,0,0,0,,See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,2:36:30.49,2:36:32.49,default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,2:36:33.57,2:36:35.57,default,,0,0,0,,SAKURAZAKA NO UTA
Dialogue: 0,2:36:51.26,2:36:53.26,default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's not like that
Dialogue: 0,2:36:53.31,2:36:55.31,default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know
